text.tspan: The proceeds of sales of DoD-purchased materials, labor, and assets shall be recouped on the basis of a
sale to "Another Federal Agency," as prescribed in DoD 7220.9-M, chapter 26 (reference (h)). This
procedure excludes capital investment costs. Such costs may be paid from recyclable material sales
proceeds in their entirety. Therefore, amortization of capital items is not applicable.
